title: Hats Off 1936 (Comedy, Music) Mae Clarke, John Payne, Helen Lynd

sources.title: Hats Off 1936 (Comedy, Music) Mae Clarke, John Payne, Helen Lynd
sources.description:
Rival press agents Jimmy Maxwell and Jo Allen have both been assigned to stir up publicity for separate exhibitions at the 1936 Texas Centennial.
 
Director: Boris Petroff
Writers: Edmund Joseph, Samuel Fuller
Stars: Mae Clarke, John Payne, Helen Lynd 
Genres: Classics, Comedy, Music
